premise_source_doc_sentence: The Citadelle Laferrière or , Citadelle Henry Christophe , or simply the Citadelle  (  Citadel  )  , is a large mountaintop fortress in Nord , Haiti , located on top of the mountain Bonnet a L'Eveque , approximately 17 mi south of the city of Cap-Haïtien , 10 mi southwest of the Three Bays Protected Area , and 5 mi uphill from the town of Milot .
